        "TileImage": "$($repository cdf72773-a822-4eb4-84f0-cc49918d6d9f).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47.\rYour destination today is Mumbai,India.\rThere is a large building under construction right in the centre of this town. Our client, who wanted to open his large business nearby, asked us to do everything possible to stop this construction in order to remove possible competitors.\r We learnt that three people-Kabib Lal, Seema Kanti and your main target Arya Vasu - give away the most funds to the building company. Kill them in a way that makes it look like an accident.\rGood luck.",
